1. Molim vas da *ostanete* ovde dok ne završim razgovor sa vašim advokatom. (Please *stay* here until I finish talking to your lawyer.)
2. Ako *ostanete* još malo, uskoro će biti gotova večera. (If you *stay* a little longer, dinner will be ready soon.)
3. Ukoliko želite da *ostanete* konkurentni na tržištu, morate redovno pratiti trendove. (If you want to *remain* competitive on the market, you need to keep up with trends regularly.)
4. Da li ćeš *ostanuti* u Beogradu ili se vratiti u rodni grad? (Will you *stay* in Belgrade or return to your hometown?)
5. Ne znam kako *ostanete* smireni u ovakvim situacijama. (I don't know how you *manage to stay* calm in situations like this.)
6. Želim da *ostanete* ovde do kraja koncerta. (I want you to *stay* here until the end of the concert.)
7. Nadam se da ćete *ostati* zadovoljni našom uslugom. (I hope you will *be satisfied and stay* with our service.)
8. Kako da *ostanem* u formi kada stalno sedim na poslu? (How can I *stay* fit when I sit at work all day?)
9. S obzirom na situaciju, ne znam koliko će ljudi *ostati* na proslavi. (Given the situation, I don't know how many people will *stay* at the party.)
10. Hoće li se deca *ostanuti* u vrtiću dok mi obavimo neke poslove? (Will the kids *stay* at daycare while we do some errands?)